[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> 3. WRONG FIELD SEPARATOR FOR groups.dat
[?2004l[?2004h>    - File uses colon delimiter (gid:name:description)
[?2004l[?2004h>    - Script used awk default (space/tab) so whole line became $1
